{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":577,"text":"Almost two years ago,"},{"time":2432,"text":"I was driving in my car in Germany,"},{"time":4823,"text":"and I turned on the radio."},{"time":7339,"text":"Europe at the time was in the middle"},{"time":9546,"text":"of the Euro crisis,"},{"time":10989,"text":"and all the headlines were about European countries"},{"time":15235,"text":"getting downgraded by rating agencies"},{"time":18076,"text":"in the United States."},{"time":19930,"text":"I listened and thought to myself,"},{"time":22039,"text":"\"What are these rating agencies,"},{"time":24111,"text":"and why is everybody so upset about their work?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":27564,"text":"Well, if you were sitting"},{"time":29616,"text":"next to me in the car that day"},{"time":31377,"text":"and would have told me that I would devote"},{"time":33939,"text":"the next years to trying to reform them,"},{"time":37183,"text":"obviously I would have called you crazy."},{"time":41131,"text":"But guess what's really crazy:"},{"time":43033,"text":"the way these rating agencies are run."},{"time":46062,"text":"And I would like to explain to you"},{"time":47705,"text":"not only why it's time to change this,"},{"time":49806,"text":"but also how we can do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52984,"text":"So let me tell you a little bit"},{"time":54638,"text":"about what rating agencies really do."},{"time":58216,"text":"As you would read a car magazine"},{"time":60600,"text":"before purchasing a new car"},{"time":62402,"text":"or taking a look at a product review"},{"time":64494,"text":"before deciding which kind of tablet or phone to get,"},{"time":68371,"text":"investors are reading ratings"},{"time":70571,"text":"before they decide in which kind of product"},{"time":73884,"text":"they are investing their money."},{"time":75972,"text":"A rating can range from a so-called AAA,"},{"time":78783,"text":"which means it's a top-performing product,"},{"time":81726,"text":"and it can go down to the level"},{"time":84253,"text":"of the so-called BBB-,"},{"time":87267,"text":"which means it's a fairly risky investment."},{"time":90692,"text":"Rating agencies are rating companies."},{"time":93253,"text":"They are rating banks."},{"time":94503,"text":"They are rating even financial products"},{"time":96867,"text":"like the infamous mortgage-backed securities."},{"time":99942,"text":"But they can also rate countries,"},{"time":102019,"text":"and these ratings are called sovereign ratings,"},{"time":104767,"text":"and I would like to focus in particular"},{"time":107124,"text":"on these sovereign ratings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109750,"text":"And I can tell, as you're listening to me right now,"},{"time":112156,"text":"you're thinking,"},{"time":113615,"text":"so why should I really care about this, right?"},{"time":116223,"text":"Be honest."},{"time":117808,"text":"Well, ratings affect you."},{"time":120097,"text":"They affect all of us."},{"time":122259,"text":"If a rating agency rates a country,"},{"time":125564,"text":"it basically assesses and evaluates"},{"time":128839,"text":"a country's debt"},{"time":130240,"text":"and the ability and willingness of a country"},{"time":132589,"text":"to repay its debt."},{"time":134930,"text":"So if a country gets downgraded by a rating agency,"},{"time":137863,"text":"the country has to pay more"},{"time":139940,"text":"in order to borrow money"},{"time":141547,"text":"on the international markets."},{"time":143108,"text":"So it affects you as a citizen and as a taxpayer,"},{"time":145909,"text":"because you and your fellow countrymen"},{"time":148272,"text":"have to pony up more in order to borrow."},{"time":152062,"text":"But what if a country can't afford to pay more"},{"time":154878,"text":"because it's maybe too expensive?"},{"time":157715,"text":"Well, then the country has less available"},{"time":160650,"text":"for other services, like roads, schools, healthcare."},{"time":164312,"text":"And this is the reason why you should care,"},{"time":166751,"text":"because sovereign ratings affect everyone."},{"time":169797,"text":"And that is the reason why I believe"},{"time":171458,"text":"they should be defined as public goods."},{"time":174414,"text":"They should be transparent, accessible,"},{"time":177226,"text":"and available to everyone at no cost."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181807,"text":"But here's the situation:"},{"time":183853,"text":"the rating agency market is dominated"},{"time":185997,"text":"by three players and three players only --"},{"time":188970,"text":"Standard &amp; Poor's, Moody's, and Fitch --"},{"time":191749,"text":"and we know whenever there\nis a market concentration,"},{"time":194706,"text":"there is really no competition."},{"time":196505,"text":"There is no incentive to improve"},{"time":198782,"text":"the quality of your product."},{"time":201099,"text":"And let's face it, the credit rating \nagencies have contributed,"},{"time":205348,"text":"putting the global economy on the brink,"},{"time":208193,"text":"and yet they have to change the way they operate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211978,"text":"The second point,"},{"time":213851,"text":"would you really buy a car"},{"time":215873,"text":"just based on the advice of the dealer?"},{"time":219359,"text":"Obviously not, right? That would be irresponsible."},{"time":222372,"text":"But that's actually what's going on"},{"time":224965,"text":"in the rating agency sector every single day."},{"time":228843,"text":"The customers of these rating agencies,"},{"time":231592,"text":"like countries or companies,"},{"time":234079,"text":"they are paying for their own ratings,"},{"time":236505,"text":"and obviously this is creating"},{"time":238503,"text":"a conflict of interest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241374,"text":"The third point is,"},{"time":243890,"text":"the rating agencies are not really telling us"},{"time":246805,"text":"how they are coming up with their ratings,"},{"time":249443,"text":"but in this day and age,"},{"time":251283,"text":"you can't even sell a candy bar"},{"time":253159,"text":"without listing everything that's inside."},{"time":256207,"text":"But for ratings, a crucial element of our economy,"},{"time":259891,"text":"we really do not know"},{"time":261560,"text":"what all the different ingredients are."},{"time":264042,"text":"We are allowing the rating agencies"},{"time":265988,"text":"to be intransparent about their work,"},{"time":268690,"text":"and we need to change this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270752,"text":"I think there is no doubt that the sector"},{"time":273232,"text":"needs a complete overhaul,"},{"time":274949,"text":"not just a trimming at the margins."},{"time":277459,"text":"I think it's time for a bold move."},{"time":279682,"text":"I think it's time to upgrade the system."},{"time":282798,"text":"And this is why we at the Bertelsmann Foundation"},{"time":285360,"text":"have invested a lot of time and effort"},{"time":288182,"text":"thinking about an alternative for the sector."},{"time":291913,"text":"And we have developed the first model"},{"time":294512,"text":"for a nonprofit rating agency for sovereign risk,"},{"time":299670,"text":"and we call it by its acronym, INCRA."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304126,"text":"INCRA would make a difference"},{"time":305524,"text":"to the current system"},{"time":307951,"text":"by adding another nonprofit player to the mix."},{"time":312153,"text":"It would be based on a nonprofit model"},{"time":315602,"text":"that would be based on a sustainable endowment."},{"time":319246,"text":"The endowment would create income"},{"time":321370,"text":"that would allow us to run the operation,"},{"time":323787,"text":"to run the rating agency,"},{"time":325489,"text":"and it would also allow us"},{"time":327539,"text":"to make our ratings publicly available."},{"time":331224,"text":"But this is not enough to make a difference, right?"},{"time":333927,"text":"INCRA would also be based on"},{"time":335800,"text":"a very, very clear governance structure"},{"time":338378,"text":"that would avoid any conflict of interest,"},{"time":341300,"text":"and it would include many stakeholders from society."},{"time":346169,"text":"INCRA would not only be a European"},{"time":348718,"text":"or an American rating agency,"},{"time":350849,"text":"it would be a truly international one,"},{"time":353213,"text":"in which, in particular, the emerging economies"},{"time":356330,"text":"would have an equal interest, \nvoice and representation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361454,"text":"The second big difference that INCRA would make is"},{"time":364884,"text":"that would it base its sovereign risk assessment"},{"time":367862,"text":"on a broader set of indicators."},{"time":370558,"text":"Think about it that way."},{"time":372459,"text":"If we conduct a sovereign rating,"},{"time":374303,"text":"we basically take a look at"},{"time":375920,"text":"the economic soil of a country,"},{"time":378587,"text":"its macroeconomic fundamentals."},{"time":381172,"text":"But we also have to ask the question,"},{"time":383350,"text":"who is cultivating the economic soil"},{"time":386266,"text":"of a country, right?"},{"time":388186,"text":"Well, a country has many gardeners,"},{"time":390346,"text":"and one of them is the government,"},{"time":392164,"text":"so we have to ask the question,"},{"time":394209,"text":"how is a country governed?"},{"time":395523,"text":"How is it managed?"},{"time":397109,"text":"And this is the reason why we have developed"},{"time":399279,"text":"what we call forward-looking indicators."},{"time":402370,"text":"These are indicators that give you"},{"time":404037,"text":"a much better read about"},{"time":405544,"text":"the socioeconomic development of a country."},{"time":409095,"text":"I hope you would agree it's important for you to know"},{"time":411853,"text":"if your government is willing to invest \nin renewable energy and education."},{"time":419034,"text":"It's important for you to know"},{"time":420759,"text":"if the government of your country"},{"time":422762,"text":"is able to manage a crisis,"},{"time":424724,"text":"if the government is finally able to implement"},{"time":427705,"text":"the reforms that it's promised."},{"time":431433,"text":"For example, if INCRA would rate"},{"time":433300,"text":"South Africa right now,"},{"time":435254,"text":"of course we would take a very, very close look"},{"time":438711,"text":"at the youth unemployment of the country,"},{"time":441011,"text":"the highest in the world."},{"time":443549,"text":"If over 70 percent of a country's population"},{"time":446993,"text":"under the age of 35 is unemployed,"},{"time":450584,"text":"of course this has a huge impact on the economy"},{"time":453680,"text":"today and even more so in the future."},{"time":457974,"text":"Well, our friends at Moody's,"},{"time":460249,"text":"Standard &amp; Poor's, and Fitch will tell us"},{"time":462572,"text":"we would take this into account as well."},{"time":465605,"text":"But guess what? We do not know"},{"time":467554,"text":"exactly how they will take this into account."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470571,"text":"And this leads me to the third big difference"},{"time":472922,"text":"that INCRA would make."},{"time":474626,"text":"INCRA would not only release its ratings"},{"time":477420,"text":"but it would also release its indicators"},{"time":480391,"text":"and methodology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":482053,"text":"So in contrast to the current system,"},{"time":484616,"text":"INCRA would be fully transparent."},{"time":488131,"text":"So in a nutshell,"},{"time":489970,"text":"INCRA would offer an alternative"},{"time":492172,"text":"to the current system of\nthe big three rating agencies"},{"time":495598,"text":"by adding a new, nonprofit player to the mix"},{"time":499563,"text":"that would increase the competition,"},{"time":501967,"text":"it would increase the transparency of the sector,"},{"time":504530,"text":"and it would also increase the quality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":507335,"text":"I can tell that sovereign ratings"},{"time":509303,"text":"may still look to you like this very small piece"},{"time":512527,"text":"of this very complex global financial world,"},{"time":516802,"text":"but I tell you it's a very important one,"},{"time":519242,"text":"and a very important one to fix,"},{"time":521684,"text":"because sovereign ratings affect all of us,"},{"time":524827,"text":"and they should be addressed and should be defined"},{"time":528365,"text":"as public goods."},{"time":529825,"text":"And this is why we are testing our model right now,"},{"time":532709,"text":"and why we are trying to find out if it can"},{"time":535636,"text":"bring together a group of able and willing actors"},{"time":538839,"text":"to bring INCRA to life."},{"time":541489,"text":"I truly believe building up INCRA"},{"time":544100,"text":"is in everyone's interest,"},{"time":546491,"text":"and that we have the unique opportunity right now"},{"time":550061,"text":"to turn INCRA into a cornerstone"},{"time":552630,"text":"of a new, more inclusive financial system."},{"time":557025,"text":"Because for way too long,"},{"time":559593,"text":"we have left the big financial players on their own."},{"time":563285,"text":"It's time to give them some company."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566081,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":568115,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}